==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mellone
<hw>Mel"lone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A
yellow powder, <chform>C6H3N9</chform>, obtained from certain
sulphocyanates. It has acid properties and forms compounds called
<xex>mellonides</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mellonide</ent>⟦br⟧
